assessments.title: Static coordinate assignment for all declarations
Introduce generic functor interface for protocol bundles
Provide algebraic structures for representing and manipulating ambiguity in parse spaces.
Establish metric structures on semantic spaces for distance/similarity calculations.
Define compositional transformation operations on semantic objects.
Implement functorial mappings between semantic and computational spaces.
Integrate 2D gating logic (Tension/Resonance) into parser and protocol records, explicitly cross-referencing ambiguity, metricization, transformation system, and functorial constructs.
Implement topological inflation: upgrade crowded semantic categories to higher-dimensional polytopes to relieve tension.
Implement Mitosis Engine to monitor topological tension and inflate categories to dynamic polytopes as needed.
Integrate Earley parsing, RoPE, and symmetry group concepts into a unified topological parser. Treat syntax as a manifold and ambiguity as vector superposition.
